<paragraph id="8BD936B5FFFF1B26FF0C6D8EE541DFA9" blockId="2.[151,1437,968,2003]" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">
<emphasis id="B912EAA7FFFF1B26FF0C6D8EE506DEB5" bold="true" box="[199,323,1688,1714]" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">Bionomics</emphasis>
. 
<materialsCitation id="3B0E3CE8FFFF1B26FE9F6D8FE4BADFA9" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3762948304" collectingDate="1938-10" collectionCode="ZSM" country="China" county="In" elevation="3000" location="October" municipality="Adults" pageId="2" pageNumber="145" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Sikkim">
<collectingCounty id="62B84E39FFFF1B26FE9F6D8FE52EDEB4" box="[340,363,1689,1715]" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">In</collectingCounty>
<collectingCountry id="F3717625FFFF1B26FEBE6D8EE5FEDEB5" box="[373,443,1688,1714]" name="China" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">China</collectingCountry>
, the male specimens were collected at high altitudes 
<quantity id="4C9E9B50FFFF1B26FBE96D8EE035DEB5" box="[1058,1136,1688,1714]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="145" unit="m" value="3000.0">
<elevation id="004BD186FFFF1B26FBE96D8EE035DEB5" box="[1058,1136,1688,1714]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="145" unit="m" value="3000.0">3000m</elevation>
</quantity>
at a temperature reaching -3.094°C (the daily average temperature was 4.887°C) and an air humidity 23.66% (
<figureCitation id="135D2A30FFFF1B26FBA66DAAE086DED1" box="[1133,1219,1724,1750]" captionStart="FIGURE 14" captionStartId="5.[151,250,1800,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,1223,1777]" captionTargetId="figure-41@5.[151,1435,1131,1777]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 14. The habitat of Arcilasisa sobria: China, Xizang, Linzhi City, Bayi Town, N29°40'01'', E94°20'24'', 3000m, 15.XI.2020 (photo by Chen Enyong)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6521554" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6521554/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">Fig. 14</figureCitation>
), while the female specimen was collected at an altitude 
<quantity id="4C9E9B50FFFF1B26FDF26DF6E6C3DEFD" box="[569,646,1760,1786]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.903" pageId="2" pageNumber="145" unit="m" value="3903.0">
<elevation id="004BD186FFFF1B26FDF26DF6E6C3DEFD" box="[569,646,1760,1786]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.903" pageId="2" pageNumber="145" unit="m" value="3903.0">3903m</elevation>
</quantity>
at a temperature reaching -5.612°C (the daily average temperature was 0.662°C) and an air humidity 64% (
<figureCitation id="135D2A30FFFF1B26FDFF6C12E6CFDF18" box="[564,650,1796,1823]" captionStart="FIGURE 15" captionStartId="6.[151,250,988,1012]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,181,964]" captionTargetId="figure-19@6.[151,1435,181,964]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 15. The habitat of Arcilasisa sobria: China, Xizang, Linzhi City, Sejila Mountain, N29°39'4.5'', E94°42'51.5'', 3903m, 15.XI.2021 (photo by Yin Xiongyan)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6521556" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6521556/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">Fig. 15</figureCitation>
). 
<collectingMunicipality id="6BBDACCFFFFF1B26FD546C12E6AFDF19" box="[671,746,1796,1822]" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">Adults</collectingMunicipality>
are on wing from 
<location id="8EB9606EFFFF1B26FC086C12E058DF19" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03CF87A3FFFF1B26FF5C69ECE70DDFD5:8EB9606EFFFF1B26FC086C12E058DF19" box="[963,1053,1796,1822]" country="China" county="In" municipality="Adults" name="October" pageId="2" pageNumber="145" stateProvince="Sikkim">October</location>
to mid-November. 
<location id="8EB9606EFFFF1B26FB356C12E16FDF19" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03CF87A3FFFF1B26FF5C69ECE70DDFD5:8EB9606EFFFF1B26FB356C12E16FDF19" box="[1278,1322,1796,1822]" country="China" county="In" municipality="Adults" name="The" pageId="2" pageNumber="145" stateProvince="Sikkim">The</location>
specimen from 
<collectingCountry id="F3717625FFFF1B26FF1E6C3EE55DDF45" box="[213,280,1832,1858]" name="Nepal" pageId="2" pageNumber="145">Nepal</collectingCountry>
deposited in 
<collectionCode id="ED77AE70FFFF1B26FE646C3EE5ACDF45" box="[431,489,1832,1858]" country="Germany" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/4b7r-7sec" name="Bavarian State Collection of Zoology" pageId="2" pageNumber="145" type="Museum">ZSM</collectionCode>
has the collecting date in 
